Requirements
Volunteers must be able to walk up and down porches.
 
Perks
As we are a non-profit organization, these hours are eligible for volunteer hours at school as well as community service.
 
Health and Safety
 This is a contact-less volunteer activity. Communication happens via email or phone. A box of leaflets and a map will be mailed to you via Canada Post. You distribute the leaflets in mailboxes without contact with residents, on your own time.

